@startuml facility-lifecycle
title Facility Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Location & Name defined

Draft --> Requested : Submitted for Vertical Review
Requested --> Approved : Ownership & Geo-link verified

state Approved {
  [*] --> Active
}

Active --> Restricted : Service Hold (e.g., Staff shortage)
Active --> Suspended : Governance Hold
Active --> Deprecated : Facility Replaced

Deprecated --> Archived : Historical Reference
@enduml
